Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade  In a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:37.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:07.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:11.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:17.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:32.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to keep fighting so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:35.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s your purpose?\NWhy did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:39.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My purpose is to save Rukia Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:47.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn’t it just this spring that\Nshe went missing in the human world?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:50.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s too short.\NIt’s a shallow friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:53.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would hardly think\Nthat’s worth risking your life for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:58.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true I know nothing about her…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And that it may fall short of\Nbeing worthy of risking my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:09.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, Ichigo wants to save her!\NSo that’s enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:14.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t need any other reason\Nto risk my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, what a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:21.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you’re that determined,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then it would be insulting\Nto ask you to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:28.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:34.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I guess I’ll have to take your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:02:59.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:19.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What does the Ritei-tai want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:23.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If they wish to give me orders,\Nthe Hell Butterfly should have sufficed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:28.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… However,\Nit's because this message is signed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:34.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,by both Head Captain Yamamoto\Nand Captain Hitsugaya of Squad Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:36.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Signed by both captains?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a top priority order?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you can do, run?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:31.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down… Calm down…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can get him.\NThere’s no way I can’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll let you take the first swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can cut me up anywhere you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:42.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can go for my neck,\Nmy gut, my eyeball…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:48.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you want,\Nyou can even kill me with this attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:50.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop quivering! Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:09.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way… I know I swung down\Nwith all my might.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:14.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that…\Nthere’s not even a scratch on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:17.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that…\Nmy hand’s split instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:24.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey… Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I’m not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t run around so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:56.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t like\Nplaying tag with weaklings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:40.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:08.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…! Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:16.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hit him…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hit him…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn’t cut him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:26.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mean there’s such\Na great difference in power between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:28.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… Calm down…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no reason for me\NNOT to be able to cut him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:37.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m just overwhelmed\Nby his Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:42.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I calm down and sharpen\Nmy Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:45.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there’s no reason I can’t cut him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even Old Man Zangetsu said it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down…calm down…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:52.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down… calm down… calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rid yourself of fear… Look to the fore…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can win… I can win…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat and you will age…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hesitate and you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can win…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:57.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad’s Spiritual Pressure…is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:14.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be…\NChad has lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is he dead? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:24.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad can’t have lost…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:34.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who’d have thought his final attack\Nwould be this powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I’d taken a direct hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:40.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it could have been really bad for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:46.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s amazing for any human to\Neven get into Seireitei,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but to think he could fight this hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kyoraku!\NWe have a message!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:59.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NIt's not like you to be out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:00.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,one of the boys from Ritei-tai was here,\Nwasn’t he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Aizen has…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:10.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,passed away…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:16.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The cause of death was removal\Nof his Saketsu Chain and Hakusui,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and destruction of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn’t an accidental death.\NHe was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is a top-priority message
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:32.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,signed by both Head Captain Yamamoto\Nand Captain Hitsugaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so I don’t believe there is any mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shosuke was…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:47.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go and see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad… Chad…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad… Chad…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:06.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Captain Kyoraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:22.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This Ryoka isn’t dead, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:28.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I deliver the final blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:39.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I deliver the final blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Girls shouldn’t\Ndo things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:07.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the person who killed Captain Aizen\Nwas probably one of the Ryoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:09.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:13.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:16.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…I’m just talking about possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:21.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, there’s no need to be\Nin such a hurry to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s call the rescue squad\Nand have him put into a cell somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:29.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If there’s the possibility that\None of them is the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,all the more reason to keep him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:39.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will make the arrangements at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:43.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for trying to meddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:50.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Things seem to have gotten\Nquite out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:54.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s faint…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but his Spiritual Pressure is still there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:11.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. What am I hesitating for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose here…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad…and Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:21.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and Ishida…and Ganju…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:23.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and Hanataro…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:24.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:30.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All the people who have\Nlent me their strength…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They’ll all die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:36.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I haven’t got any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:51.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, finally you show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:59.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or, have you just given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:05.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Both of those…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,are wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me…Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll beat this guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and I swear…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I swear…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will…save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:41.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t feel like dying yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,everything on my shoulders\Nwill be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can cut him…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:54.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:56.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know I can fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:00.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:07.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it if you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let your guard down yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay…sharpened like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:22.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the fun begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:24.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:27.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:37.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny seems so happy…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:57.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sosuke Aizen, Captain of Squad Five,\Nhas passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:03.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When he was lowered from the wall,\Nhe was no longer breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:07.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any possibility of a gigai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:08.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:15.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I investigated every possibility,\Nincluding the chance that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:18.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,someone had used a gigai\Nto deceive others’ eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:24.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it only served to confirm\Nthe truth of his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:29.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After this wartime chaos is resolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a new captain of Squad Five will\Nbe selected
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:35.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,by the Central 46 and Squad leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:42.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad Seven Captain Komamura…\NSquad Nine Captain Tosen…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:46.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Would you two please return\Nto command your squads?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:50.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I too…shall visit the front lines soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your efforts,\NCaptain Tosen…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:06.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Komamura…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:15.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did Captain Unohana say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:18.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just that Captain Aizen had passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:24.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to inquire into the truth\Nbehind Captain Aizen’s death,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:29.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it seems the quickest route lies\Nin ending this fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then…that means…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I will join the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:40.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing would be better\Nthan to avoid fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:45.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems things aren’t\Ngoing to go so smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If not for fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,people would not be mislead\Nby ugly emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and neither would ugly tragedies occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:03.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it is time for\NCaptain Tosen’s “suzumushi” to cry out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:07.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I detest fighting…\Nfrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good… Good reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your concentration is improving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:54.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike earlier,\Nyou can actually hear my bells ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wear the bells and my eye patch
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:01.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,just so I can get greater enjoyment\Nout of my battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:06.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no reason for me to wear them\Nif you don’t take advantage of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:10.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You take me for a fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:14.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And that’s why you won’t release\Nyour Zanpaku-to, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:19.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize?\NMy sword can cut you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you let your guard down and --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My Zanpaku-to doesn’t have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:27.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My sword is out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:30.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It has never had a sealed form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:36.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the true form of my Zanpaku-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:41.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Well, that’s a relief to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:46.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that means your sword won’t get\Nany more powerful than it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:47.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“In that case,” what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:55.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll be able to win soon.”\NIs that what you thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one taking me for a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:02.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I don’t seal\Nmy Zanpaku-to is that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:06.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my Spiritual Pressure is so huge\Nthat I can’t seal it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even if I use all my might.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:14.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, when I fight, I make it a habit to\Nhold back when I swing my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:16.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:20.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn’t do that,\Nmy enemies are so weak that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:23.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn’t have enough time\Nto enjoy the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:33.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to let up, didn’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On your Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:40.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Loosening up just because\Nyou found a chance or two of victory…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:54.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a boring ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:05.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And it had been a long time…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:09.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,since I came up against someone\Nwho could have killed me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or could hear my bells during battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No fun at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:31.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Damn! Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:35.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t want to die! Don’t want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How can I die in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:40.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,afford to…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Move…! Move, body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:53.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,fight one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:58.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:03.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,save Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:41.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up into the night sky\Nand saw a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:48.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you right now,\Nbut I can't fly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:56.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:22:01.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would fly across the sky… I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:08.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would circle the skies and shine over you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:13.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this instantaneous light\Nthat will definitely reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:21.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.20,0:22:24.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll always stay close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:26.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:36.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that, Ichigo?!\NThis is the strength of our Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:39.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't over yet!\NI'm going to turn things around now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:40.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:42.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-That is… Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:44.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:45.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny, looks so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:47.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!